				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "This AD plays during the Ketheric Showdown in the lower Colony. After Ketheric, in his Apostle form, calls his Necromite minions to him, they will sacrifice themselves to Ketheric, who will then gain the ability to use \"Finger of Death\". This ability does a lot of damage on its target, and will at this point in the game likely be a one-hit kill."
				}
